replies.body:
Hello Opheriaux!  When you say "where you are", do you mean my slot where my icon and name appear on champion select?  If so, we have that!  We use a bright yellow color to call out your name and highlight where you are on the screen.
If I'm getting confused, though, I'd love to know more about what you mean :)

{{champion:74}}

Give me the *option* to keep the Friends' list up. Sorry, I don't want to see all the people on my friends list when I'm not in a game. You're just going to encourage me to remove everyone off of there aside from my IRL friends.

&nbsp;

Also I want the ability to appear offline. I don't want to be visible when someone is mass-inviting, especially when they do it often.


&nbsp;

Be careful about how much socializing you're pushing. You forget at the end of the day that most of us *do* enjoy playing the game by ourselves.
